quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,O you who believe! Let neither your possessions nor your children distract you from the remembrance of God. Whoever does that—these are the losers
  63,10,"And give from what We have provided for you, before death approaches one of you, and he says, “My Lord, if only You would delay me for a short while, so that I may be charitable, and be one of the righteous.”"
  63,11,But God will not delay a soul when its time has come. God is Informed of what you do